====Usage notes====
* Alongside the traditional pronunciation {{IPAchar|/ɑ̃.kɔ.ɲyʁ/}} exists the alternative {{IPAchar|/ɑ̃.kwa.ɲyʁ/}} — this the indubitable result of {{IPAchar|/wa/}} being the typical French pronunciation of the digraph "oi." Conversely, the traditional pronunciation has also facilitated the development of the alternative spelling {{m|fr|encognure}}. Both alternatives, orthographic and phonetic, are proscribed to varied extent by traditionalists.
